articles.author: Issam AHMED
articles.title: Scientists find chemical that stops locust cannibalism - Phys.org
articles.description: Plagues of locusts that darken the skies and devastate all things that grow have been recorded since Biblical times, and today threaten the food security of millions of people across Asia and Africa.
